{"tid":326092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那父母掩護孩子搭霸王機 累全機等5粒鐘","createTime":"2017-07-17T16:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T04:26:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d02ff8f278470a8c007f7dfe84e3e4539d8e23c5","tid":326092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170717/56966394\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170717%2F56966394&d=ufi%2FbvJ5JefyUmEdKwOPs9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=96b230e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170717%2F56966394&h=bab1d1b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170717/56966394</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170717/large/1500293093_751b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170717%2Flarge%2F1500293093_751b.jpg&h=c6a17ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京機場驚爆安全隱患。昨天上午，一班由北京飛往上海的吉祥航空HO1252航班，因有小孩未有購票而登機，全部乘客要重新安檢登機，最終航班延誤5小時。<br />\n<br />\n同機乘客今日透露，當事乘客為一家五口，爸媽帶着三個孩子，其中身高不足1.2米孩子就是那個未有買票的乘客，機組人員在機艙內點算人數時發現。然而經過安檢閘口和登機關口，職員未有發現該名小孩。<br />\n<br />\n首都機場透露，當天有一名兒童在未購票的情況下，由同行成年人掩護通過安檢前的驗票閘口，並正常進行安檢後登機。登機後，經機艙服務員核對，發現有兒童在未購票的情況下登機。為了飛行安全，機場相關工作人員組織全機旅客下機重新安檢，並對該飛機進行清倉檢查。<br />\n<br />\n另有網友亦描述事發情況，指原訂於6時55分從北京首都機場飛往上海虹橋機場的航班，臨起飛前突然查出多一名乘客。現場照片中，一架吉祥航空客機停在停機坪上，客梯下圍着一些身穿制服的地勤和機務人員，疑似當事兒童剛剛下機。事後飛機被延誤了5小時才能起飛。"},{"pid":"f486615e9dc0f79222eda587baa6983d447ebb2b","tid":326092,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4b6695191d577690dbf59c13db7d211a221d24","tid":326092,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:32:19.000Z","msg":"未夠1.2米唔洗買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658d1f30dd619b54516db61c7765d29f5ad8386a","tid":326092,"uid":75033,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:41:45.000Z","msg":"見到呢啲死大陸鳩 明明自己做埋啲on9野仲要好撚無辜咁撚樣就火都黎埋 唔理大人小朋友都係"},{"pid":"ee4973e5b7585f11e18dc68747c0657c25d7fc5c","tid":326092,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:43:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未夠1.2米唔洗買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將佢寄艙囉"},{"pid":"60cb64e87d84a366b1b3ea3286169dde59749581","tid":326092,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到呢啲死大陸鳩 明明自己做埋啲on9野仲要好撚無辜咁撚樣就火都黎埋 唔理大人小朋友都係</blockquote><br />\n俾佢搞到delay 5粒鐘先係最撚無辜"},{"pid":"b02517245147e741c2a25d48122c30cc78b7ba96","tid":326092,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:44:23.000Z","msg":"外國恐怖份子又有一個參考睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1780e50261b5b0d7097f402fb5b9114dcc7678f9","tid":326092,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:48:32.000Z","msg":"就算偷到雞,上到去可以坐邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3084cae15c0970c36d95bf83dae72abb3136fb","tid":326092,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T18:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算偷到雞,上到去可以坐邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗佢地駁唔滿掛 <strong></strong>"},{"pid":"25e10bd2604a43ff8f0535a3d891311e91bbeb7a","tid":326092,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"支那狗<img src=\"/assets/fa